<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
<script src="../js/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>

<style>
map{
	width: 50%;
	height: 50%;
	margin : 0px auto;
}

#map img{
	display: block;
	margin : 0px auto;
}

h1{
	text-align : center;
}

#bus1{
	color : green;
}

#bus img{
	width : 40px;
	height : 40px;
	display: inline-block;
}

#sub1{
	color : blue;
}

</style>


<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){
	padding();
	
	$(window).resize(function() {
		padding();
	});
})

function padding(){
	bodyWidth = $('body').width();
	imgWidth = $('img').width();
	paddingWidth = (bodyWidth - imgWidth) / 2 + 'px';
	$('.pad').css('margin-left', paddingWidth);
}
</script>

</head>
<body>

<h1>대전 본사</h1>

<div id="map">
	<img  src="../images/intro/DHA 애견호텔 지도.png" alt="DHA 애견호텔 지도.png">
	<div class="pad">
		<h2>대전 중구 계룡로 846 3층 DHA애견호텔&nbsp[오류동 175-13]</h2>
		<h4>TEL.042-222-8202 &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp FAX.042-222-8202</h4>
	</div>
	<br>
</div>

<hr> <br>

<div id="bus">
	<div class="pad" style="display: flex;">
		<div style="display: flex; margin-right: 60px; width:140px;">
			<img src="../images/intro/버스 이미지.png" alt="버스 이미지.png" style="margin-top: 20px;">
			<h3 id="bus1" style="margin: 30px 0 0 10px;">시내버스</h3>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h4 style="margin-bottom: 0;">서대전네거리역4번출구역</h4>
			<h4 style="margin-top: 5px;">101번, 103번, 607번</h4>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="pad" style="display: flex;">
		<div style="display: flex; margin-right: 60px; width:140px;">
			<img src="../images/intro/지하철 아이콘.png" alt="지하철 아이콘.png" style="margin-top: 20px;">
			<h3 id="sub1" style="margin: 30px 0 0 10px;">지하철</h3>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h4 style="margin-bottom: 0;">오룡역</h4>
			<h4 style="margin-top: 5px;">1호선</h4>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div>
	
</div>


</body>
</html>
